##Assembly instructions
------
### Part II: assembling the casing

Starting where we have left off with the circuit:
The circuit is build on the base and the back panel with switch is attached to the base.
- Now attach the two side panels to the base.
</br>
![step1](https://github.com/FOSH-following-demand/Open-source-Centrifuge-for-WetLab/blob/jannes_dev/documentation/building/Step%201%20after%20circuit_%20attach%20side%20panels.jpg?raw=true)

- Connect the wires to the motor (see circuit schematic)
</br>
![step2](https://github.com/FOSH-following-demand/Open-source-Centrifuge-for-WetLab/blob/jannes_dev/documentation/building/step%202_%20wire%20motor.jpg?raw=true)

- Attach the middle panel to the sides and back

- Attach the little front panel too
</br>
![step3](https://github.com/FOSH-following-demand/Open-source-Centrifuge-for-WetLab/blob/jannes_dev/documentation/building/step%203_%20attach%20middle%20and%20front%20panel.jpg?raw=true)

- Mount the display and rotary knob to the display panel.
![step4.1](https://github.com/FOSH-following-demand/Open-source-Centrifuge-for-WetLab/blob/jannes_dev/documentation/building/step%204.1%20mount%20display%20and%20knob.jpg?raw=true)
![step4.2](https://github.com/FOSH-following-demand/Open-source-Centrifuge-for-WetLab/blob/jannes_dev/documentation/building/step%204.2.jpg?raw=true)

- Wire the display and rotary knob (see circuit schematic)
![step5](https://github.com/FOSH-following-demand/Open-source-Centrifuge-for-WetLab/blob/jannes_dev/documentation/building/step%205_%20wire%20display%20and%20knob.jpg?raw=true)
##### Tip:
Tape the wire connectors together to keep them in the right order when you have to disassemble parts.

- Screw the display panel in place
![step6](https://github.com/FOSH-following-demand/Open-source-Centrifuge-for-WetLab/blob/jannes_dev/documentation/building/step%206_%20fasten%20display%20panel.jpg?raw=true)

- Assemble the lid
![step7](https://github.com/FOSH-following-demand/Open-source-Centrifuge-for-WetLab/blob/jannes_dev/documentation/building/Step%207_%20assemble%20lid.jpg?raw=true)

- Assemble the hinges: from outside to inside: screw, spacer ring, lid/box, spacer ring, hinge, spacer ring, bolt.
- Keep the bolt on the lid a bit loose, tighten the bolt on the bottom.

![step8.1](https://github.com/FOSH-following-demand/Open-source-Centrifuge-for-WetLab/blob/jannes_dev/documentation/building/step%208.1_%20assemble%20hinges.jpg?raw=true)
![step8.2](https://github.com/FOSH-following-demand/Open-source-Centrifuge-for-WetLab/blob/jannes_dev/documentation/building/stp%208.2.jpg?raw=true)
